{
  "stem": "21731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All dresses were made at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got models from Paris, and I got one fur coat for the day and one fur coat for the evening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, naturally, I had a beautiful engagement ring, which I showed off while I was in Vienna to all my school friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was very proud of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so the trousseau was the-- the trousseau was nearly ready.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was nearly all done in monasteries-- the nuns and the pupils there-- with beautiful stitching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never later saw such embroideries and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, the blankets came from Carlsbad, because in Czechoslovakia, they were the best blankets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Something came from England, the-- you have no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was really-- I laughed about it, because I couldn't believe it every time something else arrived at my uncle's home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I was still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The wedding was fixed for the 9th of December, 1927.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That means two and-- two months and a week after I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He wanted to marry so soon, because he had his practice in-- he was an x-ray specialist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And his practice was in Krynica, a spa, with lots of winter sports.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the winter season was just beginning December, so-- and he wanted, naturally, to take me as his wife.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nothing else would [LAUGHS] do-- not at this time, and not with the Schutz, and the Parnus, and Bernstein family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the wedding was in the temple, under the chuppah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The glass was-- what you call it-- stamped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my title later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a very good lunch at my-- at my-- not my uncle's house, but the Emil Parnus house, which arranged all my trousseau and showed off what they can do.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
